    Perseus looked around the room and saw that almost everyone was
there.  He leaned over the comm unit and pushed a button.

    &quot;Kenzo, the briefing is now starting.  I can have Salveo turn on
the comm unit in the medicalbay so you can hear, or you can come up
here.

    &quot;Maximals, we have received a disturbing report from the
authorities in the port that they had sighted an unknown bot in the
port.  They sent us this image.&quot;

    Perseus reached over and hit a couple buttons on the holotable,
bringing up a 3D image of a heavily armed  dinosaur bot.  The bot had
a bright red scope-like eye and had little or no flesh.  It was
practically a living skeleton.

    &quot;Our sensors have identified this bot as Predacon.

    &quot;At my request, the atlantian authorities have ordered an
evacuation of the area to refuge shelters.  Any questions before I
move on to strategy?&quot;

